track_notes: Drive to approx mile 12.5 on Reddington Road (washboard dirt road) and park at the clearing where the Arizona Trail crosses the road.  Take the AZT on the left (East side) of the parking area towards Italian Spring.  Trail goes all the way up but there are many side trails so be careful to stay on the correct course.  This is a long hike, my GPS read 10.2 miles up with 4,822 feet elevation gain.
track_title: Mica Mountain Up via Italian Spring
